{{version030}}
{{flavour|Causes the water around or under the target to violently swirl, dealing damage. It can affect targets standing in or flying above water.}}

'''Waterstrike''' is a monster-only spell which deals heavy, [[smite-targeted]] physical damage which ignores [[EV]]. It can only be used on targets on a [[water]] tile (shallow or deep), though it can be used on [[flying]] targets.

The following enemies cast Waterstrike:

{{monsterlink|Water nymph}}

==History==
*Waterstrike was added in [[0.14]].

[[Category:Monster spells]]
